---

# 1Ô∏è‚É£4Ô∏è‚É£ DOCUMENT IMMUTABILITY & ARCHIVING

After approval:

* Invoice locked
* Version history frozen
* Stored in secure archive
* Retention policy applied

Retention may follow regulatory standards (e.g., 5‚Äì10 years).

---

# 1Ô∏è‚É£5Ô∏è‚É£ EXCEPTION HANDLING WORKFLOW

If mismatch detected:

```
Invoice Flagged
    ‚Üì
Exception Ticket Created
    ‚Üì
Assigned to Review Officer
    ‚Üì
Supplier Notified (if needed)
    ‚Üì
Resolution Logged
```

Resolutions may include:

* Adjustment
* Credit note
* Rejection
* Re-submission

All steps auditable.

---

# 1Ô∏è‚É£6Ô∏è‚É£ CREDIT NOTE & ADJUSTMENT LOGIC

System supports:

* Partial invoice approval
* Credit note issuance
* Refund tracking
* Adjustment linking to original invoice

Maintains financial traceability.

---

